content:
Assign a Softphone Layout to a User Profile

When you have defined one or more custom softphone layouts, you can assign them to user profiles.

Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs) and Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To assign a softphone layout to a user profile:

From Setup, enter Softphone Layouts in the Quick Find box, then select Softphone Layouts.
Click Layout Assignment.
Select the softphone layout for each user profile.
Click Save.

Call center users will see their newly assigned softphone layout the next time they log into Salesforce.
title: Assigning Custom Softphone Layouts in Service Cloud
